{"id": "1447164614310629550", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "克系的恐懼感是建立在無法理解上（未知）\n從人類的倫理道德觀來看大自然的話確實很多東西都無法理解，可以說是最接近生活的克系（", "timestamp": "2025-12-07T09:55:31.070000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
