{"id": "1447166098423287858", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "1383559917591592981", "author_name": "ququ12358", "author_bot": false, "content": "形容得可以，之前有看过类似的海洋生物视频，深海的那些乌贼他们的眼睛有篮球差不多的大小", "timestamp": "2025-12-07T10:01:24.910000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1447165465775571046", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
