{"id": "1447166453651476560", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "我們深海界域的好夥伴升級素材海百合，想要了解他們演化有多誇張的我推薦這個影片，他講得很好笑\n\nhttps://youtu.be/SBd9IZbGQw8?si=doHskiBqs5ybeCL9", "timestamp": "2025-12-07T10:02:49.603000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "海百合：一朵自由的奇葩", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SBd9IZbGQw8", "description": "它迈着鬼畜的步伐，演化成了一朵奇葩\n\n很高兴你找到了【芳斯塔芙】👏欢迎订阅👏 https://reurl.cc/eOGVxx\n\n这里是个生物泛科普频道，会分享有趣的知识～\n『芳斯塔芙 & 鬼谷藏龙，为您带来fun stuff』\n\n💗喜欢我的视频欢迎点赞评论分享💗\nThanks For Watching, Like, Comment ..."}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1447167021325484133", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "真的是大的能跟人頭差不多大。\n好喜歡深海⋯⋯陸地生物的體型生長會被環境限制，但海裡可不管你那麼多⋯⋯重點是人類對於深海的了解甚至還不如宇宙⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2025-12-07T10:05:04.947000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1383559917591592981"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1447166098423287858", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1447167183376351437", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1383559917591592981", "author_name": "ququ12358", "author_bot": false, "content": "对，最直接的例子就是鲸鱼", "timestamp": "2025-12-07T10:05:43.583000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
