{"id": "1447168431760867479", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "還是因為陸地上無可避免的需要考慮到重力對身體結構的影響吧\n水裡有浮力只要能解決生存和呼吸問題其他基本隨便（", "timestamp": "2025-12-07T10:10:41.221000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1447169882688065607", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1383559917591592981", "author_name": "ququ12358", "author_bot": false, "content": "演化还是有其自有的道理，非常自然\n克苏鲁一看就是那种非常突兀的", "timestamp": "2025-12-07T10:16:27.149000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
